A vintage-style technical illustration featuring a classic red Swiss Army knife floating in space, with each of its tools transforming into flowing streams of data ribbons in XML blue, JSON gold, and binary green. The knife hovers above an intricate mechanical canvas or blank parchment, with the data streams weaving and painting abstract patterns onto it. The background has an aged paper texture with subtle gear mechanisms and circuit-like filigree borders. Warm sepia tones dominate with pops of jewel-colored data streams. The composition suggests transformation and versatility, with the traditional tool evolving into something more flexible and powerful. Atmospheric lighting creates depth, with soft shadows and metallic reflections on the knife's surface.
